          </p>
          <p>
            Your presence and generosity helped us celebrate our first graduating class of yoga teachers while supporting our mission to bring wellness to underrepresented communities in Chicago.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Heart Emoji Decoration */}
        <div class="mt-10 flex justify-center gap-4 text-4xl animate-pulse-slow">
          <span>üíõ</span>
          <span>üôè</span>
          <span>üíõ</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    {/* END: Hero Section */}

    {/* START: Fundraising Results Section - Static */}
