        </div>

        {/* Notice about professional photos */}
        <div class="mt-10 inline-block bg-gradient-to-r from-vibrant-pink/10 to-accent-gold/10 rounded-xl px-6 py-4 border border-accent-gold/20">
          <p class="text-medium-gray font-body">
            <span class="text-vibrant-pink font-semibold">Note:</span> These are first look photos. Professional photography will be shared soon!
          </p>
        </div>
